text: Bichurino () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Bichurinskoye Rural Settlement, Bardymsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 1,373 as of 2010. There are 32 streets. == Geography == It is located 13 km south-west from Barda. == References == Category:Rural localities in Bardymsky District
title: Bichurino
